# Sentry crash reporting — optional, disabled unless a DSN is set here at build time.
#
# amont only reports crashes when a DSN is baked into the build. Builds from source have none
# (this example file is never read), so they send nothing — that is the default.
#
# To enable it in your own release builds: copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and set your
# Sentry DSN below. Reports are opt-out at runtime from the home screen; they carry no
# repository contents, diffs, or credentials, and no PII (IP, hostname, user identity).
MAIN_VITE_SENTRY_DSN=
